#My first Python lab in my CIS129 course
#This story is about Peanut the Pomeranian from Tucson, Arizona. He goes on a adventure with his brother Nemo. Nemo is a shy grey tabby cat who loves to sleep and eat. There adventures have taken them all over the country, and Peanut loves to include Nemo in his mischevious activities. One day they will  eventually settle down, calm down a bit, think about all of their adventures. They are truly partners in crime, and the best of friends.
